ru.cos.sim.visualizer.frame
Class ViewableObjectInformation

java.lang.Object
  ru.cos.sim.visualizer.frame.ViewableObjectInformation

public class ViewableObjectInformation
extends Object

Representation of the double-linked list's element. Main goal of this class - containing information about objects, that are on screen. The first element in the list - is head element. Head element can be indicated by isHead variable.

Author:
Dudinov Ivan
